Revenge Is Not A Game | ClearMind | 2025 Thriller Movie | Best New Thriller Movies \ best 2025 Movies

Revenge isn't confined to reality; it can thrive in the depths of your thoughts. In the gripping thriller "ClearMind," a woman immerses herself in virtual reality therapy to confront her traumatic past. As she navigates this digital realm, she discovers an unexpected avenue to turn the tables on her former friends. However, as therapy begins to merge with obsession, the boundary between healing and vengeance becomes dangerously thin.

2025.  Stars: Rebecca Creskoff, Toks Olagundoye, Jenn Lyon
